  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Starting with <i>v</i> &minus; 5 = 8/(<i>w</i> &minus; 4), multiply both sides by (<i>w</i> &minus; 4): (<i>v</i> &minus; 5)(<i>w</i> &minus; 4) = 8. Divide by (<i>v</i> &minus; 5): <i>w</i> &minus; 4 = 8/(<i>v</i> &minus; 5). Add 4: <i>w</i> = 8/(<i>v</i> &minus; 5) + 4.</p>",
